title: CCK Podcast: Let Your Trash Flag Fly (featuring @KellyKeegs)
description:
Kelly Keegs officially joins the Barstool roster! If you are trash, embrace it. You can love leftovers and above ground pools, you just have to admit that you are trash. What is you ideal first date? Catch Cutting Stems, Kelly's new show where she teams up with Ria, Fran, and Trent to bring you live show instant reactions to every episode in the Bachelor/Bachelorette universe. Every week, following the Bachelorette, starting Tuesday, Oct 13th (if no NBA Finals Game 7) on Barstool channels.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
